Feature: Searching for a local eSIM
          As an end user
          In order to connect to the internet
          I want to find and buy a local eSIM


  Scenario: eSIM search for Canada
    Given I am on the Airalo homepage
    And Local eSIMs tab is active by default
    When I search Airalo for Canada
    Then I should see Canada's eSIMs listed as a Local option
    And I close the browser

  Scenario: eSIM search for Africa
    Given I am on the Airalo homepage
    When I tap on Regional eSIMs Tab
    Then I should see Africa, Asia, Carribean Islands, Europe, Latin America, Middle East and North Africa regions
    And Regional tab becomes active
    When I search for Africa
    Then I should see Africa's eSIMs listed
    And I close the browser

  Scenario: Search for Global eSIM
    Given I am on the Airalo homepage
    When I tap on Global eSIMs Tab
    Then I should see Global eSIMs listed
    And Global tab becomes active
    And I close the browser


